summary: It's interesting that Villanelle thinks she loves Eve. Firstly, she's a malignant psychopath, so we know that's not true. At...
body: It’s interesting that Villanelle thinks she loves Eve. Firstly, she’s a malignant psychopath, so we know that’s not true. At least, her brand of love isn’t congruent with the understanding and concept of love that people who don’t have empathy deficit disorders subscribe to anyhow. Secondly, I strongly suspect Villanelle isn’t in love with Eve at all. She’s infatuated with Eve’s fascination with her, which is much more fitting for what we know of psychopaths. Still, it’s interesting that Vilanelle believes this to be love.
